### Describe the bug

nix-shell/nix-build fails with hardly explainable error: "infinite recursion encountered" if there is a typo in cabal module name i.e. executable depends on referrers "external module".


### Steps To Reproduce

html-conduit-demo-a.cabal:
```
name:                html-conduit-deom-a
...
executable elf
  main-is:             Elf.hs
  hs-source-dirs:      elf
  Build-Depends:       base >=4 && <5, html-conduit-demo-a
```

default.nix:
```
